sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Controller Manager<br/>Service Account Token
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant VirtualService as Istio VirtualService
    participant Knative as Knative Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Agent as Agent Sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant EventSink as Event Sink<br/>80/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>kubectl apply -f isvc.yaml<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate InferenceService<br/>API Server cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated/Defaulted CR
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event notification
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>Service Account Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService & DestinationRule<br/>Service Account Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over StorageInit,ModelServer: Flow 2: Model Loading
        StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/Secret Key
        S3-->>StorageInit: Model files
        StorageInit->>ModelServer: Write to /mnt/models<br/>Shared Volume
        ModelServer->>ModelServer: Load model into memory
        ModelServer->>K8sAPI: Report readiness
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 3: Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>VirtualService: Route by host header
        VirtualService->>Knative: Forward to Service<br/>mTLS client cert
        Knative->>Agent: HTTP request<br/>localhost:8080
        Agent->>ModelServer: Proxied request<br/>localhost:8080
        ModelServer-->>Agent: Prediction result
        Agent-->>Knative: Response
        Knative-->>Gateway: Response<br/>mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response
        Agent->>EventSink: Request/Response log<br/>Bearer Token (if enabled)
    end
